casebody.data:
The COLORADO INDEPENDENT, petitioner,
v.
DISTRICT COURT FOR the EIGHTEENTH JUDICIAL DISTRICT OF COLORADO, et al. No. 18-404. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 19, 2019.

Motion of respondent Sir Mario Owens for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Motion of respondent District Court of Colorado for leave to file a supplemental appendix under seal granted.

*1166Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Colorado denied.
